article_id:88,category_name:Maintenance,title_name:Maintenance on Nov 14[Addendum],image_path:,message:<div>We are planning to undergo maintenance during the following period in order to adjust the rewards of the daily bonus, quests and endeavors.</div><div><br></div><div>*Rewards cannot be obtained if you complete a quest during the maintenance period.</div><div>*Please remember to pick up the daily reward from the 7-Day Pack (Resources) or 30-Day Recovery Pack before maintenance begins, if you have purchased either.</div><div><br></div><div>■Maintenance Period</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1542259800"></span> ～ <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1542262200"></span></div><div><br></div><div>■Details</div><div>1. The rewards for each of the daily endeavors below will be changed as follows:</div><div>・Clear Avenue to Power: 5,000 mana instead of 3,000 rupies</div><div>・Perform an Item Summon: 6 gold crystals instead of 1,500 mana</div><div>・Collect Rupies from a Facility : 3 gold whetstones instead of 1 silver whetstone</div><div>・Clear a Quest Playing Co-op: 300 eldwater instead of 100 eldwater</div><div>・Clear Five Quests: 1 exquisite honey instead of 1 blessed water</div><div><br></div><div>2. The rewards of the daily bonus will be changed as follows:</div><div>Day 1: 5,000 mana instead of 1 quality Honey</div><div>Day 2: 5,000 mana instead of 3,000 mana</div><div>Day 4: 20,000 rupies instead of 10,000 rupies</div><div>Day 8: 2 exquisite honey instead of 1 exquisite honey</div><div><br></div><div>3. The rewards for the event quest Clear Avenue to Power will be increased.</div><div>・The amount of crystals Fafnir drops will be increased at all difficulty levels.</div><div><br></div><div>4. Clear Avenue to Fortune will be added to the daily endeavors</div><div>・The reward for clearing this endeavor will be 5 blessed water.</div><div>・The amount of rupies dropped at all difficulty levels will be increased.</div><div><br></div><div>5. Some adventurers&#39; skill damage will be increased.</div><div><br></div><div>As a gift for bearing with the change to the daily bonus, we are sending out 3 quality honey (changed the name from exquisite honey, which was incorrect) to all players who started the game before <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1542261600"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>This notice will be updated when the items have been distributed.</div><div><br><span style="color: rgb(41, 105, 176);"><strong>[Addendum <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1542198600"></span>]</strong></span><br>The following point in paragraph 3 was incorrectly announced as a planned adjustment, and was consequently removed from the list:<br>・The amount of adventurer EXP earned by clearing the quest [Clear Avenue to Power] will be increased.<br><br></div><div>■Notes</div><div>1. The game will be inaccessible during maintenance.</div><div>2. The maintenance times above may vary.</div><div><br></div><div><span style="color: rgb(41, 105, 176);"><strong>[Addendum<span class="local_date" data-local_date="1542261660"></span><br></strong></span>The maintenance is now complete.<br><br>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1542024000,update_time1542364408